{"tid":1561172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外媒指 6 藏人逃離中國遭尼泊爾拘留　送交中國警察","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T13:43:18.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8741e37bfa8e7ce3f9f58825e09b5d229a1d9eb2","tid":1561172,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202019-09-1120at208.48.1720PM_0xAt8_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202019-09-1120at208.48.1720PM_0xAt8_1200x0.png&h=666e1b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《自由亞洲電台》引述消息人士，指尼泊爾政府上周四（5日）將六名剛逃出中國境、尋求庇護的西藏人拘留，當時他們大聲哭叫，哀求警方不要把他們交回中方，當地民眾亦為他們求情不果，最後警方將他們送交至中國警察手上。<br />\n<br />\n其中一位匿名人士於當地從事貿易，他對《自由亞洲電台》西藏分部記者表示，這六名西藏人上周四到達尼泊爾邊境時，遭尼泊爾警方拘捕，並將他們鎖上手扣帶至位於西北部、 旅遊朝聖重地 Simikto 的警署，同日傍晚將他們交到中國邊防警察手上，「當時他們大聲哭叫，哀求（尼泊爾）警方不要把他們交與中方」。<br />\n<br />\n該六名西藏人由中國西藏自治區普蘭鎮，進入尼泊爾邊境，消息人士形容他們臉色紅潤、身穿西藏服飾，指當時很多當地民眾看到他們被鎖上手扣被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n第二名居於首都加德滿都的消息人士指，當地警方把六人帶走時，並阻止民眾接近，警方同日把他們交給中國當局，又警告他們不要把此消息傳開，被發現的話，將會面對嚴重後果，「當時那些西藏人多番哀求，稱他們是到尼泊爾尋求庇護，當地民眾也求情，要求警察釋放他們不果，警員面露不耐煩」。<br />\n<br />\n尼泊爾與西藏比鄰， 1959 年西藏發生反抗漢人統治的武裝叛變，遭解放軍鎮壓，逾 2 萬名西藏人逃離中國，在當地居留至今。中國政府迫使西藏精神領袖達賴喇嘛與 8 萬西藏人，流亡至印度北部喜馬拉雅山脈的達蘭薩拉（Dharamsala）地區。<br />\n<br />\n尼泊爾堅持「一個中國」政策，認為西藏是中國的一部分，並打壓當地流亡藏人。 7 月初，尼泊爾政府以安全為由，拒絕當地藏人為今年 84 歲的達賴喇嘛，舉辦慶祝生日活動。6 月時，加德滿都機場移民局，拒絕讓一名來自西藏的美國公民入境，並把他遣返，據報是出於中國要求。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E6%8C%87-6-%E8%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%83%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%AD%E5%B0%BC%E6%B3%8A%E7%88%BE%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99-%E9%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258C%2587-6-%25E8%2597%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2580%2583%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%25B3%258A%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%258B%2598%25E7%2595%2599-%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%2F&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=f386d7ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258C%2587-6-%25E8%2597%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2580%2583%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%25B3%258A%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%258B%2598%25E7%2595%2599-%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%2F&h=0ddeae65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E6%8C%87-6-%E8%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%83%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%AD%E5%B0%BC%E6%B3%8A%E7%88%BE%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99-%E9%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F/</a>"},{"pid":"9892049416164bc6710789d490d18e2ac66a6404","tid":1561172,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1586b5535ee40c9de600f4e4f422cba01deb3309","tid":1561172,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:34:34.000Z","msg":"唔